              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".BACKGROUND FROM THE O-16(N,P)N-16 REACTION CAPTURE",
                " GAMMA RAYS (2.2 MEV) AND FROM IMPURITIES IN THE TANK,",
                " AMOUNTING TO 1-5 PERC., DRIFTS IN STABILITY OF THE",
                " ELECTRONICS (ABOUT 1 PERC), DEAD TIME EFFECTS,",
